msgid ""
msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "Greetings, citizens of Kamurocho.\r\nPardon the interruption. It will only be a moment."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "What is this...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "I urge you all to stop\r\nand listen to what I have to say."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "As you may know, this city has been\r\ninfected by a vile group called the Saio Triad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "Since their arrival, Kamurocho has\r\nbecome host to an endless conflict."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "If we wish to rid ourselves of them, we need\r\na strong voice to force them out. <font_kind=yakuza_italic>Your</font_kind> voice."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "The first step is ensuring they know\r\nwe will not stand for their criminal acts."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "We must boycott their nerve center, Little Asia.\r\nDo not line their pockets by shopping there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "Further, I suggest you stay away for\r\nyour own safety as well. If you don't..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "...You may just find yourself on\r\nthe receiving end of something like this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "Hm...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "Wh-What's going on!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "Have I made myself clear?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "To fund them is to be complicit.\r\nEven those who pay them for \"protection.\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "If you wish to live, cut all ties with the Saio Triad.\r\nOnly then will our city be cleansed of them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "Kamurocho is ours.\r\nIt is about time we prove it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "Urgh... That trash bag...\r\nWhat did I do wrong...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "I don't get it... Why?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "Hey, are you okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "That blast looked pretty strong.\r\nAre you hurt?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "I-I think I'm okay, yeah...\r\nYou saw it, too?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "I thought that bag was suspicious..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "I didn't think it'd actually explode, though...\r\nThere must've been a bomb in there!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "The bag, huh...\r\nThere's no way to trace it, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "I saw the guy, though!\r\nI watched him put that bag there!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "What...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "It was a guy in his 40's wearing a yellow tracksuit.\r\nPretty sure he was Chinese."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "Chinese? Wait, was he with the Saio?\r\nThe guy on the screen was against them, though..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "I don't have a clue."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "\r\nAll I know for sure is I heard the guy who\r\nput that trash bag there speaking Chinese."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "And where did you hear him?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "Over at the Yoshida Batting Center."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "Thanks for the info."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "That trash bag exploded!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "I saw the whole thing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "Hm? You there.\r\nYou want to hear about the explosion, too?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "Well, the bomb went off right next to me.\r\nI thought I was done for..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "I remember.\r\nI was around here when it happened."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "Really!? You were there, too?\r\nThen, I'll tell you..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "The guy who planted that bomb was definitely Chinese.\r\nHe was in a yellow tracksuit over at the batting center."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "(So the guy who planted the bomb\r\nis over at the batting center...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "(He should be wearing a yellow tracksuit.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "What you want?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "You're Chinese, right?\r\nAre you with the Saio Triad?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "Excuse me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "I've run into all sorts of Chinese here,\r\nbut every one of them was Saio."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "I not part of Saio Triad.\r\nI no think like them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "Well then... who are you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "You say who you are first!\r\nWe only just meet, but you annoy me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "Somebody told me they saw you leaving\r\na black trash bag over on Tenkaichi Street."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "I was there when the bag exploded.\r\nI saw everything."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "You planted that bomb, didn't you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "Who tell you they saw me there?\r\nWas it information desk guy?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "What if it was?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "I knew it, he looking at me whole time.\r\nNow he know my face."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "I shut him up later.\r\nBut now, I shut you up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "Who <font_kind=yakuza_italic>are</font_kind> you!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "That's what I want you to tell me.\r\nIf you're not Saio, who are you with?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "Planting bombs isn't exactly a civilian thing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "You think I give up that easy?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "Get back here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "That's it. It's time you tell me the truth.\r\nWho are you with if not the Saio Triad?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "Even if I tell you, you no know their name."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "Go on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "Our group famous in Kamurocho many years ago.\r\nBack then, we even as strong as Tojo Clan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "My group called Snake Flower Triad!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "Snake Flower...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "Right, I remember you guys.\r\nIt's been a while since I've heard that name."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "You... know Snake Flower Triad?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "They were the most brutal mafia in town,\r\nled by a guy named Lau Ka Long."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "Yes, exactly!\r\nOh man, I so happy now!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "Lau tried to murder me when I was still a\r\njunior Dojima Family man. I'm Kazuma Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "Kiryu? Kazuma Kiryu!?\r\nYou're... really him!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "So you guys are back in Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||||4"
msgid "Are there any more of you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "86||||4"
msgid "Not really. Our leader is guy in mask\r\nwho was on the big screen before explosion."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||||4"
msgid "Right. Makes sense."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||||4"
msgid "Long ago, you crush Snake Flower Triad.\r\nNow I here in Japan to rebuild from ground up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "89||||4"
msgid "Rebuild?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||||4"
msgid "If only Lau Ka Long still alive.\r\nMaybe this go well then. But..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||||4"
msgid "Snake Flower officers realize their planning very poor.\r\nSo, they lose interest in Japan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||||4"
msgid "They lose interest in us, too.\r\nNobody even remember we here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||||4"
msgid "Your superiors literally forgot about you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||||4"
msgid "We no have money to go back home.\r\nDay after day, we live here alone in this city."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||||4"
msgid "Then Saio Triad arrives in Kamurocho.\r\nThey come later than us, then ignore us!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96||||4"
msgid "Now <font_kind=yakuza_italic>they</font_kind> at war with Tojo Clan.\r\nBarely know Snake Flower exists! So humiliating!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "97||||4"
msgid "Wait just a sec...\r\nDo I have this straight?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "98||||4"
msgid "The reason you set off that bomb...\r\nis so people would notice you? Really?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||||4"
msgid "We want to make Saio Triad pay\r\nfor embarrassment they cause us!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||||4"
msgid "...I almost understand how slighted you feel,\r\nbut you need to stop antagonizing the Saio."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||||4"
msgid "<font_kind=yakuza_italic>I</font_kind> managed to find you with barely any effort.\r\nImagine how easy it would be for them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||||4"
msgid "You wouldn't even stand a chance.\r\nThey'd slaughter you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||||4"
msgid "Ah... Dammit!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||||4"
msgid "It's up to you... but don't throw your lives away.\r\nI'll look past the bomb thing... this time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "106||||4"
msgid "I don't have time to deal with this nonsense.\r\nJust go back to leading honest lives."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||||4"
msgid "Kazuma Kiryu, the Dragon of Dojima.\r\nWe cannot defeat him now... We lose."
msgstr ""

